data.title: Urgent Care Now Webster
data.meta_description: Urgent Care Now in Webster, NY has been serving patients since March 2, 2009. Our goal is to provide fast, affordable, quality care that stands out from the rest. We have helped over 95,000 patients in our region.
data.text:
We want to thank the community for their support through these trying times. We want to assure all, that we will continue to serve this community and our patients with the best care we have always offered.

As of May 3rd, 2020 we have returned to our normal hours.

A special thank you to those who have supported us with supplies and mask. Your support and warm thoughts will not go unnoticed.

We will continue to be here for you, when life happens!

According to the CDC please follow same precautions used during flu and cold seasons. Wash your hands often, stay home when you’re sick and avoid contact with people who are ill, will help to keep the risk of this virus low in our area. If you feel flu-like symptoms and have recently traveled to an area experiencing significant outbreaks of the virus, you should Contact Your Doctoror the New York State Hotline for further instructions.

New York State Hotline 1-888-364-3065
